      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>KONOVITCH-Bernyce. Age 75 on July 24. School teacher for over 25 years in West Simsbury, CT. Beloved wife of Rabbi Harold Konovitch. Loving mother of Jonathan, David and Robyn. Adored motherin-law, grandmother, aunt and cousin. She touched us all. Shiva through July 31 at Konovitch home, 48 Bradford Rd, Scarsdale</p>
